Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.43,0:00:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.44,0:00:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.09,0:00:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.44,0:00:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.55,0:01:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.49,0:01:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.74,0:01:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,妳忘了最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的事?你指的是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.20,0:01:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.17,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第一次見到妳時,就一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.08,0:01:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是,以後也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.23,0:02:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#93 春天的預感?\N兩人的熾熱心情!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要沮喪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會為你舉辦安慰宴會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.76,0:02:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要發表\N畢業考的成績,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把結果告訴我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當…當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還在介意他跟朱美的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,完蛋了,我得延畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有補考啦,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別事不關己說得那麼輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.39,0:03:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易才找到工作耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.23,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜!別哭啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有明年!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就這樣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是又還沒確定他不能畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,總覺得會是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要我怎麼回答妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是五代打回來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,順利畢業啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.42,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,託您的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作找到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去私立幼稚園應徵看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我幫你介紹兩三家\N我認識的幼稚園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.57,0:04:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在徵人的地方很少\N你別抱太大的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.59,0:04:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我會先打個電話去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可以去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是地址和電話號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝園長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,好好加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我就來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,來人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.49,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,很久沒這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跌落吧,跌到深谷底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠無法翻身…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.07,0:06:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你在幹什麼?\N大家都在等你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.17,0:06:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣,祝五代前途無量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好的給你服務一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我心領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.09,0:06:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有打電話回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來五代果然沒有合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能沒臉回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然早就該回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧,妳也很沮喪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有喝酒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再說下去沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候非得借酒澆愁不可吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高興你還肯回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,還有明年嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.87,0:07:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託妳的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你畢業考過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位,敬五代的奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我有先準備起來\N(太好了,五代祝畢業)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.79,0:07:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就剩就業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是大問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要參加褓母考試\N這次真的要舉行安慰宴會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你們操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.97,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就要去幼稚園面試了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面試?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎實幼稚園的園長\N幫我介紹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.01,0:08:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且褓母資格考\N我一定會一次就通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你蠻有自信的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,人家介紹給你的工作\N你好像都沒被錄取過不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想得太美了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳的命也真苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個不是和好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是急死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子和好,一下子吵架\N又不是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹嘛這樣看我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.88,0:08:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道賓館的事\N是我惹出的風波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.48,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這都要怪你們不乾脆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點發生關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他又不是妳第一個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說,還是怎麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還無法忘記妳老公嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.67,0:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確無法忘記惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.18,0:09:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能因為這樣就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.52,0:09:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說,妳喜歡五代對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又使用緘默權嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寡婦就是這樣才讓人討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.83,0:09:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了一個死掉的人守貞節\N有什麼用呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.67,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為妳欺負她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她實在太不坦率了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:10:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說,我看五代這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得他好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.77,0:10:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確無法忘記惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代他不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.53,0:11:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還問什麼事,就是面試啊\N現在應該在面試了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.26,0:11:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會為了昨天的事心煩\N沒有心情面試啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,你在酒家打工?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,照顧酒家小姐的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,學校能畢業嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外關於褓母資格的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.39,0:11:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個一邊工作一邊考就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.39,0:11:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我會打電話通知你結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一位請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一位面試的人不在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-來了!\N-宏介!宏介,不要用跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.41,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉,我兒子很調皮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪到你進來面試囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好,那麼我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,爸爸要談工作的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要,我也要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,哥哥陪你玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.63,0:12:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣,大家都是來面試的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.17,0:12:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,你想玩什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當馬給我騎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當馬給你騎?這個好難哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管,你要當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再搖用力一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,別那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好玩啊?宏介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.32,0:12:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普普通通\N媽媽當馬給我騎比較舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宏介!沒禮貌!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽什麼時候會回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽已經是外人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?為什麼?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?我不要!\N我們去接她回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宏介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.03,0:13:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很丟臉,我老婆跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,別談這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,剛才的面試\N你可能會被錄取哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.41,0:13:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,園長一直在誇獎你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大男人帶著一個孩子\N一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被錄取…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果找到工作的話\N就能堂堂正正求婚,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.17,0:14:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確無法忘記惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面試結果怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.86,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,不過總感覺他很可憐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有,他在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.45,0:14:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代\N若葉幼稚園的園長打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經到家了啊,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.36,0:15:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的\N我想早點通知你比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.76,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你照顧那小孩的方式\N真的讓我很佩服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.23,0:15:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,您太誇獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的,我相信你到任何地方\N都會被錄取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次我打算錄取\N另外一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道\N他帶著一個小孩蠻可憐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,說…說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.79,0:15:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,好,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果大家的想法\N好像都一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.06,0:15:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒有立場同情他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,總覺得鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找工作這種事急不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在你理想中的工作環境工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這才是最好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說不在意\N那是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.28,0:16:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我從心裡將惣一郎抹消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我或許根本辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.02,0:16:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的確存在過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.62,0:16:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都愛惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.03,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我眼裡只有惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.33,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追逐著惣一郎的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.27,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎把我的心填得滿滿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個斷崖的地層很有意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.30,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我無法給妳同樣的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.08,0:17:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在我能力範圍內\N用我的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳帶來不同的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我能做的只有這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.87,0:17:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要同樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.54,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是惣一郎的替代品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要過來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.93,0:18:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在大家在茶茶丸\N接續昨天的第二攤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了,聽見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們等妳來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.74,0:18:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天,對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,我才不好意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係,待會見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是朱美打來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,叫我們去參加\N昨天的第二攤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺變成下雪了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說小狗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還沒餵牠吃晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.45,0:19:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你連狗的名字\N都會那麼在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.22,0:19:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確很好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到妳跟惣一郎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是感到很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\N除了我之外什麼都別想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的心情怎麼那麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,妳也那麼認為嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.04,0:21:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來特別開朗耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.67,0:21:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能跟五代之間\N發生了什麼事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.24,0:21:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.38,0:22:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫院?他哪裡不舒服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.92,0:22:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像說要去探病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.92,0:22:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式錄用?您的意思是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.96,0:22:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我閃到了腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.83,0:22:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能年紀大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加上幼稚園只有我一個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.74,0:22:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我才要請您多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.21,0:22:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.38,0:22:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.62,0:22:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次那些還有剩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.15,0:22:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.16,0:22:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳,真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.83,0:22:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.56,0:22:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳跟我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.68,0:23:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你!五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.35,0:23:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我沒聽到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.05,0:23:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,掛斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.52,0:23:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.50,0:23:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.60,0:23:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳跟我結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.71,0:23:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.62,0:23:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代求婚了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.86,0:23:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒,雖然他昨晚也練習了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.76,0:23:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,聽說管理員的爸爸極力反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.97,0:24:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還衝去酒家找他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.17,0:24:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N「太好了!五代決死的求婚」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.87,0:24:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,請妳跟我結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.28,0:24:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.95,0:24:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.15,0:24:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.09,0:24:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.37,0:24:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.47,0:24:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.21,0:24:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.05,0:24:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.75,0:24:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.06,0:25:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.90,0:25:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.64,0:25:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.45,0:25:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.72,0:25:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.99,0:25:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
